---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { Navbar } from '../components/landing/Navbar';
import { Footer } from '../components/landing/Footer';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy — Nexus AI" description="Privacy policy and data protection terms for Nexus AI workspace.">
  <Navbar client:load />

  <main class="pt-32 pb-24 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
    <article class="bg-cream-50 rounded-sm border border-ink-900/15 shadow-2xl p-8 md:p-12 vintage-border">
      <div class="vintage-divider text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-6 text-ink-500 font-sans">
        <span class="flourish text-base">✦</span>
        <span class="mx-3">Compliance & Trust</span>
        <span class="flourish text-base">✦</span>
      </div>

      <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl font-medium text-ink-900 mb-8 text-center">
        Privacy Policy
      </h1>

      <div class="prose prose-stone dark:prose-invert font-sans text-sm text-ink-700 leading-relaxed space-y-6">
        <p class="italic font-serif text-ink-500">Last updated: June 4, 2026</p>
        
        <p>
          At Aixentrix, Inc., we prioritize your trust and privacy. This Privacy Policy describes how we collect, use, process, and share your personal data when you use the Nexus AI productivity workspace.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-serif text-xl font-semibold text-ink-900 mt-8 mb-4 border-b border-ink-900/10 pb-2">
          1. Data We Collect
        </h2>
        <p>
          We only collect data necessary to provide and secure our workspace integrations. This includes:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Account Data:</strong> Name, email address, password, and profile preferences when you sign up.</li>
          <li><strong>Connected Workspace Data:</strong> Calendar events, task lists, documents metadata, and email headers only if you explicitly choose to connect those integrations to Nexus AI.</li>
          <li><strong>Usage Information:</strong> Diagnostic data, sub-second latency logs, and AI queries/actions metrics.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="font-serif text-xl font-semibold text-ink-900 mt-8 mb-4 border-b border-ink-900/10 pb-2">
          2. How Your Data is Used
        </h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>To run, maintain, and optimize your AI Chief of Staff features.</li>
          <li>To compile your daily briefings, drafts, and task assignments.</li>
          <li>To process billing, payments, and subscription renewals.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="font-serif text-xl font-semibold text-ink-900 mt-8 mb-4 border-b border-ink-900/10 pb-2">
          3. Data Security & Storage
        </h2>
        <p>
          Your data is encrypted both in transit (using TLS 1.3) and at rest (using AES-256). We are SOC 2 Type II certified and adhere to GDPR policies. Importantly, <strong>we never sell your personal data or use your documents/emails to train public foundation models.</strong>
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-serif text-xl font-semibold text-ink-900 mt-8 mb-4 border-b border-ink-900/10 pb-2">
          4. Contact Us
        </h2>
        <p>
          If you have questions about this policy or request data deletion, please contact our support team at <span class="font-medium text-ink-900">privacy@nexus-ai.com</span>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </article>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
